## Complaints
complaints.heading=What to do if you are not happy with how we respond to your complaint
complaints.p_1=The Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) is responsible for enforcing the Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No. 2) Accessibility Regulations 2018 (the ''accessibility regulations''). If you are not happy with how we respond to your complaint,
complaints.p_2=contact the Equality Advisory and Support Service (EASS)
complaints.p_3=or the
complaints.p_4=Equality Commission for Northern Ireland (ECNI)
