## In person contact
in-person-contact.heading=Contacting us by phone or getting a visit from us in person
in-person-contact.p1=We provide a text relay service if you are deaf, hearing impaired or have a speech impediment.
in-person-contact.p2=We can provide a British Sign Language (BSL) interpreter, or you can arrange a visit from an HMRC advisor to help you complete the service.
